{"tid":1451214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"812聽日入機場！","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:29.000Z","uid":38450,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"589620ced81edd83bf679e9a30834b4b79615315","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"812聽日全部人同我入機場做文宣講比國際聽今日嘅事！<br />\n<br />\n宣傳口號唔洗再講「香港加油」依啲。去得嘅大家心照，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主要係用英文宣傳比外國知</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n再者，我地要唸下遊客最有興趣係乜野。比著你係遊客，見到「Free Hong kong」未必會感興趣，因為始終依到唔係佢地屋企。但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>見到「HK Police HIT Traveler」佢地一定會睇，因為佢地自己就係遊客</strong></span>，可能會比香港警察打喎，會比心機睇發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n我地將警察推外國人，遊客跪地等照片做引入，再提出721之後香港已經被恐怖襲擊不安全，出街會比人打，吸入生化武器氣體。一步步帶佢地了解成件事。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>先用佢地會關心嘅事做引入，再令到佢地慢慢關心依件事！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得口號要同啲遊客講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong Not Safe Now, Police Hit Travelers, Police Use  Biochemical Weapons To People</span></strong></span><br />\n一下就可以吸引佢地注意力。唔好再嘻嘻哈唱今天我比到一種輕鬆嘅感覺比佢地，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果連我地當時人都唔緊張，佢地外地人點會緊張呀！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n812 機場文宣集會<br />\n1：00PM<br />\n齊向國際發聲<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8c007057788c4b8b22d3d202801fc0e5c0d825d5","tid":1451214,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家 準備長期作戰<br />\n聽日唔好再玩接機 笑笑口和理非<br />\n記住個女仔半邊面係血既樣<br />\n記住班黑警1m距離內開槍+掉人落電梯<br />\n記住依家有幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日12/8 Full gear塞爆+癱瘓 成個機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔唱歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔接機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒 統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253d00a55acd9e3e0bf861bc6f2da6cde4640e30","tid":1451214,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"聽日癱瘓機場 同遊客講既對話就係<span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港好危險 自己搵領事館救你</span>"},{"pid":"14603e102ea9b65daf52d3ed4016fff24b53f3c1","tid":1451214,"uid":287256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:41.000Z","msg":"- 北角 疑似大陸武警 大媽軍裝出現<br />\n- 北角 縱容福建黑社會襲擊記者市民<br />\n- 太古站 1米極近距離行刑式開槍 推市民落扶手電梯並且毆打<br />\n- 尖沙咀 6隻鬼帶隊召黑衫人 帶頭燒警署<br />\n- 尖沙咀 少女遭布袋彈瞄頭射爆眼球 永久失去視力<br />\n- 尖沙咀 美麗華門口掃射正逃離示威者<br />\n- 尖沙咀 襲擊醫療人員 阻止人道救授<br />\n- 屯門 市廣場無故拉人<br />\n- 旺角 解放軍救護車停泊彌敦道<br />\n- 深水埗 藏於路中心私家車 對路過示威者作出突襲拘捕<br />\n- 荃灣 白衫人圍毆路人 大叫救命無人理<br />\n- 葵芳站 站內狂射催淚彈橡膠彈<br />\n- 銅鑼灣 對被捕示威者插贓嫁禍<br />\n- 銅鑼灣 警察扮示威者射丫叉 混入人群搞事後表露身分制服旁人同時大量防暴增援<br />\n- 全港九 蓄意傷害無反抗能力之人士"},{"pid":"c2c2256b41b504498fd7edbef92735f0767cdf89","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ceb2dca60784a82cca9f92bbfed91b1bdabcb43","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b9d249594ef6b3a9877f1062d392e8ee92301ea0","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea19dfafee504daa3f3aa2d0533d737ef382acb5","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:48:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51f7f2190330b60e564369d179e903f35b1b3f3a","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ccd67533b3df56314cb3bdd44437b40e53567f3","tid":1451214,"uid":38450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eab3b409068cb0295a909e264739be8a4cfcf8ba","tid":1451214,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}